- some asset types are non-transferable

- add support for details on site types
- add support for details on site recipes
- add support for variable result site recipes
- add support for site visibility in graphql
- add support for site requirements in recipes
- add support for site visibility in recipe requirements

Resource sites

- sites have attributes that change over time
- sites only are created when they are discovered which is an action that can be done manually or by structures
- sites can disappear
- sites can be publicly visible or privately visible
- sites can be accessible to an "owner" or everybody
- sites can be associated with an asset instance